56.6929133858267775 331.6537795275589815 Td
(Many students face difficulty understanding complex academic topics, especially in subjects like) Tj
T* (Mathematics, Science, and Computer Graphics. They often do not receive immediate help when) Tj
T* (they have doubts. Traditional learning methods do not always provide personalized attention, which) Tj
T* (makes learning stressful and less effective.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0 g
56.6929133858267775 240.9451181102361943 Td
(Who is affected by this problem?) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0 g
56.6929133858267775 209.7640157480313974 Td
(The primary group affected is school students \(Grades 6–12\). Students who study independently or) Tj
T* (do not have access to extra coaching are especially impacted. Teachers are also indirectly affected) Tj
T* (because they may not be able to give individual attention to every student in a classroom.) Tj
ET
BT
/F2 12 Tf
13.7999999999999989 TL
0 g
56.6929133858267775 134.6459055118109518 Td
(How did I find out about this?) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 11 Tf
12.6499999999999986 TL
0 g
56.6929133858267775 103.4648031496061549 Td
(Interviews, Observation, AI Tools, Online Research) Tj
