(Our project is an AI-powered learning assistant designed to help students understand difficult) Tj
T* (academic topics more easily. The system provides instant doubt-solving support along with visual) Tj
T* (explanations using computer graphics. It is accessible, user-friendly, and designed to improve) Tj
T* (student confidence and academic performance. By combining Artificial Intelligence with interactive) Tj
T* (learning methods, this project aims to make education smarter and more effective.) Tj
ET
